abstract: >-
  Complete verification artifacts for 14 results produced by Demonstrandum, a
  verification-first multi-agent AI mathematics pipeline: 11 refutations of
  published conjectures, two proofs of published conjectures (Elizalde–Luo and
  Kurkov's A000670 conjecture), and one numerical record (C(13) >= 36 for the
  "no 5 on a sphere" grid problem), including Lean 4 kernel-checked proofs of
  the discrete Borsuk cube-characterization disproof and the Elizalde–Luo
  formula. Every claim is mechanically checkable via the included verify_all.py
  battery.
